Title: 103: Why this Is the Golden Age of Data Science & How to Get In
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Data Science Freelance Consultant, Emanuele Carbone. You will hear about creating a massive value with Tableau and Excel, learn how to get established as a data science consultant and learn how Emanuele went from novice to pro in just one year.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/103
